body_html:
The two 'x's by both commits suggest that neither of the emails are being detected by the CLA. The CLAbot would give a different message if all authors had signed the CLA (and that would be okay).

If your graphcore.ai is part of the googlegroup, can you also check to see that you've added that email to your GitHub account (public) ? I think that's the only other requirement.
